---
/**
 * Introduction section — brand philosophy with botanical SVG divider.
 */
---

<section class="introduction section" id="about" aria-label="About Perpetual Petals">
  <div class="introduction__inner">
    <span class="overline">Our Philosophy</span>
    <p class="body-text">
      Perpetual Petals is a private floral membership serving a limited number of homes in Windermere, Florida.
    </p>
    <p class="body-text">
      Using premium garden roses, seasonal blooms, and delicate natural greenery, every design is composed to feel airy, romantic, and quietly luxurious. Arrangements are delivered, refreshed, and exchanged on a regular cadence&thinsp;&mdash;&thinsp;allowing flowers to become a living element of your space rather than a fleeting detail.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Botanical SVG divider -->
<div class="introduction-divider" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg class="introduction-divider__svg" viewBox="0 0 160 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <line x1="0" y1="12" x2="58" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" />
    <g transform="translate(80, 12)">
      <ellipse cx="0" cy="-4" rx="2.2" ry="5.5" transform="rotate(-25)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.8" />
      <ellipse cx="0" cy="-4" rx="2.2" ry="5.5" transform="rotate(0)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.8" />
      <ellipse cx="0" cy="-4" rx="2.2" ry="5.5" transform="rotate(25)" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.8" />
      <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5" />
    </g>
    <line x1="102" y1="12" x2="160" y2="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" />
  </svg>
</div>

<style>
  .introduction {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .introduction__inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width-text, 640px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-md, 32px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .introduction__inner .overline {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .introduction__inner .body-text + .body-text {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* Botanical SVG Divider */
  .introduction-divider {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-md, 32px) 0;
    color: var(--color-rose, #855E4A);
  }

  .introduction-divider__svg {
    width: 160px;
    height: 24px;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
